OL,3,CManx businesses say hospitality sector
OL,4,Cis 'in crisis' due to rising costs
OL,6,FA number of business owners in the say
OL,7,Fthe hospitality sector is 'in crisis',
OL,8,Fas a result of rising costs and labour
OL,9,Fshortages.
OL,11,FMembers of the Licensed Victualler's
OL,12,FAssociation (LVA) met last week with
OL,13,F74 hospitality venues, after a number
OL,14,Fof businesses closed their doors for
OL,15,Fgood over the last few months.
OL,17,FMark Davison has been running 'The Tea
OL,18,FJunction' cafe in the centre of
OL,19,FDouglas for the last nine years, but
OL,20,Fhas been forced to close his doors due
OL,21,Fto financial pressures.
