OL,3,CManx businesses say hospitality sector
OL,4,Cis 'in crisis' due to rising costs
OL,6,FHe said: "I set this place up to get
OL,7,Fme out of the office nine years ago,
OL,8,Fand we did that, and it's been a
OL,9,Froaring success.
OL,11,F"And after ten years, I should be in a
OL,12,Fposition where I've got a business
OL,13,Fthat I can sell on to somebody. The
OL,14,Fbusiness just isn't worth anything
OL,15,Fbecause it's not making any money."
OL,17,FMark said the closure was a result of
OL,18,F'rising wage costs, coupled with a
OL,19,Fturbulent inflationary world'.
