OL,3,CManx businesses say hospitality sector
OL,4,Cis 'in crisis' due to rising costs
OL,6,FAndy Saunders runs the 'Quids Inn' pub
OL,7,Fon Douglas Promenade, and believes the
OL,8,Fsector is at breaking point.
OL,10,FHe said: "The Isle of Man Small, a
OL,11,Fmedium Private businesses are in
OL,12,Fcrisis at the moment. We are seeing
OL,13,Fmany of our friends and families fail
OL,14,Fbusiness wise, and it's not an issue
OL,15,Fof poorly run businesses, it's an
OL,16,Fissue that very much appears to be
OL,17,Ffrom a poorly run the economy."
