OL,3,CManx businesses say hospitality sector
OL,4,Cis 'in crisis' due to rising costs
OL,6,FIn February, the island's government
OL,7,Fannounced a rise in income tax from
OL,8,F20% to 22%, targeting what it called
OL,9,Fthe 'squeeze middle'.
OL,11,FWhen asked about the effects of the
OL,12,Fbudget, Andy said that the government
OL,13,Fhave 'disproportionately burdened our
OL,14,Flower-paid workers', adding that it is
OL,15,F'unacceptable that someone earning the
OL,16,Fproposed minimum wage of #11.45 per
OL,17,Fhour would be taxed at the new highest
OL,18,Frate of 22%.'
