OL,3,CManx businesses say hospitality sector
OL,4,Cis 'in crisis' due to rising costs
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man's Chamber has been
OL,7,Fcampaigning around how VAT, rising
OL,8,Fcosts, and labour shortages are having
OL,9,Fa 'devastating impact on the sector'.
OL,11,FThe rate of VAT in the Isle of Man is
OL,12,F20%, mirroring the UK, but different
OL,13,Fto that of the Crown Dependencies.
OL,15,FIn Jersey, it sits at 5%, while in
OL,16,FGuernsey there is no VAT or any other
OL,17,Fconsumption tax.
