OL,6,FSpeaking in the House of Keys,
OL,7,Ftreasury minister Dr Alex Allinson
OL,8,Fsaid reducing VAT rates would lead to
OL,9,Fhigher taxes elsewhere.
OL,11,FBoth he and the enterprise minister
OL,12,FTim Johnston are due to meet
OL,13,Frepresentative of the LVA on Monday.
